        <briefdescription>
<para>Register a factory for a metrics reporter type. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Thread-safe. Registrations can be performed at any time, including concurrently with <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1MetricsReporters_1a4246661863289079c323014fd4317d47" kindref="member">Load()</ref>.</para>
