<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Type" kindref="compound">Type</ref> identifier matched case-sensitively against the value of &quot;metrics-reporter-impl&quot; in catalog properties, mirroring Java&apos;s fully-qualified class-name lookup (e.g., &quot;noop&quot;). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>factory</parametername>
