    <briefdescription>
<para>Factory class for creating and managing <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1MetricsReporter" kindref="compound">MetricsReporter</ref> instances. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class provides a registry-based factory for creating <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1MetricsReporter" kindref="compound">MetricsReporter</ref> implementations. Custom reporter implementations can be registered using the <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1MetricsReporters_1accb2bcd37b640072c1dfe9bbb9cc76d9" kindref="member">Register()</ref> method. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
